Author notes
Map Name: Fy_Funtimes
Version: 1.5a Final
Created By: Stryker
Email: StrykerMikado@gmail.com
Website: http://www.elitegeneration.com/

First of many maps from me. This map is a redone version of all the snow and iceworld type maps. Ive combined the both and made it into something pretty fun. Enjoy!

Changelog:
1.5a - Fixed more textures and repositioned some brushes.
1.5 - All weapons have full ammo. Changed textures. Cubemaps.
1.4 - Fixed weapon arrangement. Fixed any leaks. Added barrels.
1.3 - Added glass for more fun.
1.2 - Everything tweaked and all leaks fixed.
1.1 - Added 4 crates to map.
